Jayde walks down the hall and is nearly run over by Riekan, who is 
burdened with a large crate of supplies.  "Yeep!" she exclaims, 
jumping out of the way.  "Where'd you get that?"

"Ask Gatara," he tells her, continuing on his way.

Jayde does just that.  Gatara gives her the story and a crate of her 
own to carry.  "If you'd been paying attention when I called you 
earlier, you wouldn't have missed everything," she adds with a glare.

"Sheesh, just because Lunara and I happen to be close ..." Jayde 
continues muttering all the way to the engine room.
